InfoSys/FreeDB $Revision: 0.92 $
===============================

SHORT DESCRIPTION

The modules in InfoSys::FreeDB form an API to query FreeDB and CDDB
databases.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Error
  File::Compare
  File::Copy
  File::Spec
  IO::File
  IO::Socket::INET
  LWP::UserAgent
  Sys::Hostname
  Test::More

